On Mon, 27 May 2002, Dan Martin wrote:

> i read that the shafts are the same, but are the c/v joints the same too.
> what we have here is both shafts out ready to to take apart and install new
> boots and repack(not in that order). what i need to know is if it makes a
> diffrence as to which c/v goes to the trans and the one that goes to the
